From 6408450d1f072697001fe96d9fab59be1a4f32e0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Faisal Khan <mfkhan@sofi.org>
Date: Thu, 9 Apr 2026 00:06:55 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 04/11] refactor(skills): restructure skills categories and
 enhance UI interactions

- Updated skill categories to reflect current technologies and frameworks, including renaming and reorganizing sections.
- Introduced a toggle feature for categories with more than five skills, allowing users to expand and view additional skills.
- Removed unused CSS styles and optimized the layout for better responsiveness and user experience.
- Updated unit tests to reflect changes in the skills component and ensure proper rendering of categories and skills.
